{"id":1160,"category_slug":"toeic","category_name":"TOEIC Listening","position":122,"title":"Conversation 62","subtitle":"Blender Return Request","level":"B1","parts":16,"url":"https://dailydictation.com/exercises/toeic/conversation-62.1160/listen-and-type","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-62-2023-09-23-21-39-08/0-conversation-62.mp3","transcript":"Hello, Mr. Scofield?\nI'm Robin Aldrin with the support team,\nand I was informed that you were having an issue.\nHow can I help?\nI was hoping I could return this blender.\nBut I was told by a customer service agent that I was not eligible for the refund\nbecause I had lost the original receipt.\nFirst of all, I want to apologize for the experience you've had.\nDid you pay with a debit or a credit card by any chance?\nYes, I paid with a Visa credit card.\nIn that case, I'll be able to scan your card to verify the purchase.\nPhew... That's a relief.\nThanks.\nNo problem.\nPlease have a seat.\nIt'll take just a few minutes for me to sort things out.","youtube_video_id":"","details_cached_at":"2026-06-15T21:00:38","challenges":[{"position":1,"content":"Hello, Mr. Scofield?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-62-2023-09-23-21-39-08/1.mp3","time_start":0.33,"time_end":2.41},{"position":2,"content":"I'm Robin Aldrin with the support team,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-62-2023-09-23-21-39-08/2.mp3","time_start":2.41,"time_end":4.89},{"position":3,"content":"and I was informed that you were having an issue.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-62-2023-09-23-21-39-08/3.mp3","time_start":4.89,"time_end":7.46},{"position":4,"content":"How can I help?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-62-2023-09-23-21-39-08/4.mp3","time_start":7.46,"time_end":8.58},{"position":5,"content":"I was hoping I could return this blender.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-62-2023-09-23-21-39-08/5.mp3","time_start":8.58,"time_end":10.94},{"position":6,"content":"But I was told by a customer service agent that I was not eligible for the refund","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-62-2023-09-23-21-39-08/6.mp3","time_start":10.94,"time_end":15.43},{"position":7,"content":"because I had lost the original receipt.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-62-2023-09-23-21-39-08/7.mp3","time_start":15.43,"time_end":17.6},{"position":8,"content":"First of all, I want to apologize for the experience you've had.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-62-2023-09-23-21-39-08/8.mp3","time_start":17.81,"time_end":21.68},{"position":9,"content":"Did you pay with a debit or a credit card by any chance?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-62-2023-09-23-21-39-08/9.mp3","time_start":21.68,"time_end":25.07},{"position":10,"content":"Yes, I paid with a Visa credit card.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-62-2023-09-23-21-39-08/10.mp3","time_start":25.07,"time_end":27.58},{"position":11,"content":"In that case, I'll be able to scan your card to verify the purchase.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-62-2023-09-23-21-39-08/11.mp3","time_start":27.58,"time_end":31.85},{"position":12,"content":"Phew... That's a relief.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-62-2023-09-23-21-39-08/12.mp3","time_start":31.85,"time_end":33.84},{"position":13,"content":"Thanks.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-62-2023-09-23-21-39-08/13.mp3","time_start":33.84,"time_end":34.53},{"position":14,"content":"No problem.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-62-2023-09-23-21-39-08/14.mp3","time_start":34.53,"time_end":35.68},{"position":15,"content":"Please have a seat.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-62-2023-09-23-21-39-08/15.mp3","time_start":35.68,"time_end":36.96},{"position":16,"content":"It'll take just a few minutes for me to sort things out.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-62-2023-09-23-21-39-08/16.mp3","time_start":36.96,"time_end":40.39}]}